long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: The WikiTree AGC (Automatic GEDCOM Cleanup) extension allows users of wikitree.com to automatically reformat biographies created by GEDCOMpare. It adds a button to the wikitree profile edit page when the profile looks like one created by GEDCOMpare. Pressing the button will reformat the biography into a chronological narrative that provides a good starting point for a typical WikiTree biography.
